_QPy6qXCA" rel=3D"" style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">O=
wnership Economy</a> isn&#8217;t just a nice-to-have; it&#8217;s an imperat=
ive. And luckily, it&#8217;s happening. We just need to get out of our own =
way: web3 regulation, accredited investor rules, onerous registration requi=
rements. All of these need to change to match the modern era.&nbsp;</p><p s=
tyle=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em=
